Johan Olof Widgren, né Pettersson (9 June 1907 – 6 March 1999) was a Swedish stage and film actor.  He won the Eugene O'Neill Award in 1967.
His granddaughter is actress Helena Bergström.


== Selected filmography ==
Ulla, My Ulla (1930)
Hem från Babylon (1941)
Only a Mother (1949)
Karin Månsdotter (1954)


== References ==
